{
  "stem": "26765.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Camp Vught was probably the worst camp for me, because I was separated from my brother for a short time.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We arrived there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were still very well nourished from all of that good food we had eaten at the convent.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so at first I couldn't eat at all, the food there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But what was so dreadful for me was the fact that I was placed in the women's camp, and George was placed with the men.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the separation was just totally devastating for me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was worse than the experience at Bergen-Belsen because I felt totally isolated, forlorn, abandoned.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I cried all the time.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I couldn't eat the food.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I couldn't understand why the other people weren't crying.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I thought there was something wrong with them, that they were not crying.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But on Sundays, George would come to visit me, and I would be so happy then.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "What I remember about Vught, initially, was that we had to take off our clothes and put them on a big pile.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they gave us something to wear, but it was so windy at that time, that I could feel the sand just scratching my legs.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And then I did find my dress again, which I was very happy about.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Evidently, it was sent to be deloused.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "At Camp Vught, shortly after I got there, I had one of the most joyful experiences also because May 11th is my birthday.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It was my eighth birthday.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And we were called to the commandant's office.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Now, that scared me a lot because the guards there, the Nazi guards, men as well as women, were very brutal.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And they would hit people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And when we'd have barrack inspection, for instance, all the beds had to be perfectly made.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
